    <title type="text">A Font Family for Susy</title>
    <id>http://andmeyer.com/2012/10/09/susy-fonts</id>
    <updated>2012-10-09T00:00:00Z</updated>
    <link href="http://andmeyer.com/2012/10/09/susy-fonts" />
    <author>
      <name>Eric A. Meyer</name>
    </author>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;The first drafts
of the &amp;#8220;GreenMud Susy&amp;#8221; fonts
are kerned, complete,
and roughly &lt;a class="reference external" href="http://greengreenmud.com/"&gt;in place&lt;/a&gt;.
Susy chapters now use her font,
&lt;span class="caps"&gt;JJ&lt;/span&gt; chapters use his,
and the remainder is split
until I flesh out a neutral &amp;#8220;narrator&amp;#8221;&amp;nbsp;font.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Susy&amp;#8217;s fonts look like&amp;nbsp;this:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;ol class="susy-fonts"&gt;
  &lt;li class="susyregular"&gt;
    &lt;strong&gt;Susy Regular:&lt;/strong&gt;
    The quick &lt;span class="amp"&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; brown fox jumps over the lazy&amp;nbsp;god.
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li class="susybold"&gt;
    &lt;strong&gt;Susy Bold:&lt;/strong&gt;
    The quick &lt;span class="amp"&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; brown fox jumps over the lazy&amp;nbsp;god.
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li class="susysc"&gt;
    &lt;strong&gt;Susy SmallCaps:&lt;/strong&gt;
    The quick &lt;span class="amp"&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; brown fox jumps over the lazy&amp;nbsp;god.
  &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

&lt;figure&gt;
  &lt;img src="/static/pictures/susy-font.jpg" alt=" " /&gt;
  &lt;figcaption&gt;
    Susy Regular in action, Chapter 18.
  &lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;figure&gt;
  &lt;img src="/static/pictures/susy-font-vector.jpg" alt=" " /&gt;
  &lt;figcaption&gt;
    Susy Bold Q, under construction.
  &lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;figure&gt;
  &lt;img src="/static/pictures/susy-font-bio.jpg" alt=" " /&gt;
  &lt;figcaption&gt;
    Susy Bold, SmallCaps, and Regular on the &amp;#8220;about&amp;#8221; page.
  &lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="caps"&gt;JJ&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#8217;s fonts (created earlier) look like&amp;nbsp;this:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;ol class="jj-fonts"&gt;
  &lt;li class="jjregular"&gt;
    &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="caps"&gt;JJ&lt;/span&gt; Regular:&lt;/strong&gt;
    The quick &lt;span class="amp"&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; brown fox jumps over the lazy&amp;nbsp;god.
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li class="jjbold"&gt;
    &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="caps"&gt;JJ&lt;/span&gt; Bold:&lt;/strong&gt;
    The quick &lt;span class="amp"&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; brown fox jumps over the lazy&amp;nbsp;god.
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li class="jjitalic"&gt;
    &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="caps"&gt;JJ&lt;/span&gt; Italic:&lt;/strong&gt;
    The quick &lt;span class="amp"&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; brown fox jumps over the lazy&amp;nbsp;god.
  &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
